                        <date>Second half of 19th century.</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; the word salām; several lines, or
                           groups of lines in the page opening the commemorative notices for each
                           month; the names of the donors; the initial line of each commemorative
                           notice; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic
                           numbers.</seg>
                     </handNote>
